APT69
osint
I parked my car, but I have forgotten where. Can you help me find it? The flag is the norwegian organisation number of the company whose car park this is. The flag matches NNS\{\d{9}\}

Brute force
osint
I just landed here, but where am I. The flag is the name of the island I landed on. An example is NNS\{Santorini\}

thehackerscrew
osint
I'm standing on top of this river next to a small town about 300m away, the mountain I'm looking at is 3060m tall and is approximately 3700m away, can you find out which town im next to? Flag: NNS{name_of_town}

osint.desc:
THEM?!
osint
Everyone is always talking about touching some grass; so I finally did. But can you tell me where the house I saw is located? The flag is the geohash (7 chars) of where the house is located. E.g. NNS{kpbpbpb}

